}}

{{quotation
|quote=No, it is not recommended due to its dependency on [https://packages.debian.org/geoclue-2.0 geoclue-2.0]. This dependency not only expands the attack surface but also raises [https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/geoclue/geoclue/-/issues/177 privacy concerns]. Currently, instructions to mitigate these risks remain [[undocumented]].
